{"tid":673722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隱形民建聯　殺入創新辦","createTime":"2018-05-22T05:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T04:25:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ede3029e94c0223f65d372489f56334fc5815c97","tid":673722,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180522/20398235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20398235&d=l5eGLvVAMMxnCWCHCGEdVIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9822a642\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20398235&h=c8366375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180522/20398235</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年05月22日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：隱形民建聯　殺入創新辦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180522/large/a08a03a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180522%2Flarge%2Fa08a03a.gif&h=759962ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n中央政策組改組為政策創新與統籌辦事處後，早前公開招聘年輕人加入做政策研究，噚日上任政策分析主任嘅其中一人為陳禧淦（圖），有指陳係「隱形民建聯」，故此惹來官場議論紛紛。<br />\n<br />\n陳禧淦曾於2013年以城大公共政策學系學生身份，聯同民建聯觀塘區議員顏汶羽喺《文匯報》發表題為〈『佔中』行動是偽公民抗命〉嘅評論文章，而陳同時係九龍社團聯會觀塘地區委員會委員之一，而委員會主任正係曾於中聯辦任職嘅觀塘區議員黃春平。<br />\n<br />\n顏汶羽向八方證實陳透過公開招聘加入創新辦，指陳曾於其地區辦事處實習，其後轉任為議辦職員、後來再到民建聯研究部工作，透露有鼓勵對方應考，體驗吓政府點做公共政策研究，相信陳獲聘與其政治背景無關，指政府取錄陳係對佢過往工作嘅認同。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：唔戰康城戰維港　影帝偉帆船賽奪亞 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n八方相當年：張仁良細個曳曳　老師扑頭 (李八方)"},{"pid":"a8515185ccbc9996747484129b50d36c317fbeda","tid":673722,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf35f19f5cd3a7c921f95907661d1f07b10e18d","tid":673722,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"依家重需唔需要隱形呀？"},{"pid":"e05ddaedecfdbe7a71b8f5557bfdaa5895629c62","tid":673722,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"顏汶羽同顏千汶有無關係"},{"pid":"9d1ac4cea832b0fca60ae11c688a9bdab02fd70c","tid":673722,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}